Ok Here is how to innstall this:

1. Just install normally

2. Open Keygen.exe

3. Select the T-racks deluxe v3.x

4. And push generate

5. Then you get the serial number witch you enter when you open T-rack for the first time.

6. Then it asks you for authorization code

7. Now go back to the very first page(just push back back back)

8. Then push the upper option

9. Select to do this on same computer

10. Select that you are not a costumer(whatever)of IK multimedia.

11. then you will get 2 codes the first on is crap a the second one is the Digital id code HURRAY!

12. Copy the digital id code that you see there into the Keygen.exe Digital id filter and push generate.

13. Now you have everything you need just re-peat 2 3 4 5 and 6
